\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The Durban University of Technology is a public higher education institution that has programmes that are accredited by the Council on Higher Education \'28CHE\'29 \line \line The Institution is currently applying for the accreditation of the Postgraduate Diploma in Tourism Management programme which will be offered in the contact mode of delivery at Durban\'2C Ritson Road\'2F Mansfield campus.\line \line The Institution has also applied for the accreditation of the Postgraduate Diploma in Ecotourism and the Diploma in Ecotourism programmes which are still in process. \line \line The Institution is accredited to offer the following programmes\'3A\line 1. Higher Certificate in Tourism H\'2FH04\'2FE109CAN \'28Contact mode of delivery \line 2. Advanced Diploma in Tourism H\'2FH04\'2FE128CAN \'28Contact mode of delivery\'29 \line 3. Diploma in Tourism H\'2FH04\'2FE110CAN \'28Contact mode of delivery \line 4. Advanced Diploma in Ecotourism H\'2FH04\'2FE129CAN \'28Contact mode of delivery\'29\cell \pard 

